===============================================
PDF TIMEOUT ERROR - 2 MINUTE FIX
===============================================

ERROR: "PDF generation timed out after 30 seconds"

===============================================
QUICK FIX (Follow Exactly):
===============================================

STEP 1: Backend Running Hai?
-----------------------------
Backend terminal check karo.

Expected:
  üöÄ Neuro360 Backend Server running on port 5000
  ‚úÖ Gemini API key present: true

Agar nahi chal raha:
  npm run dev:backend


STEP 2: .env File Banao/Update Karo
------------------------------------
Root folder mein .env file:

VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:5000/api
GEMINI_API_KEY=your-gemini-api-key-here

Gemini API key nahi hai?
  Get from: https://aistudio.google.com/apikey


STEP 3: Frontend Restart
-------------------------
Frontend terminal mein:
  Ctrl+C (band karo)
  npm run dev (phir se start karo)

Ya browser refresh:
  Ctrl + Shift + R


STEP 4: Test Backend
---------------------
Browser mein kholo:
  http://localhost:5000/api/health

Expected:
  {"status":"OK","message":"Server is running"}

Agar error:
  Backend nahi chal raha ‚Üí npm run dev:backend


STEP 5: Try Again
-----------------
1. Algorithm Processor kholo
2. Files upload karo
3. Execute calculation
4. "Save & Download" click karo

Expected:
  - Toast: "Generating NeuroSense PDF Report..."
  - Wait 30-60 seconds (Gemini AI takes time)
  - Toast: "PDF Report generated!"
  - PDF auto-downloads
  - Button: "Saved ‚úì"

===============================================
BACKEND LOGS CHECK:
===============================================

Backend terminal mein ye dikhe to sab sahi hai:

üìÑ === PDF Report Generation Started ===
üë§ Patient: John A
ü§ñ Using Gemini AI PDF Generator
üìù Generating AI-powered PDF to: neurosense-report-...pdf
‚úÖ PDF Report Generated Successfully!
üìÑ File: neurosense-report-john_a-1234567890.pdf

Agar ye nahi dikha:
  - Port mismatch hai
  - Frontend backend ko reach nahi kar pa raha

===============================================
COMMON ERRORS & FIXES:
===============================================

Error: "Failed to fetch"
  Fix: Backend start karo (npm run dev:backend)

Error: "404 Not Found"
  Fix: .env mein VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:5000/api

Error: "Gemini API key not found"
  Fix: .env mein GEMINI_API_KEY=your-key

Error: "Timeout after 60 seconds"
  Fix: Check internet connection
       Check Gemini API quota
       Wait and retry

===============================================
TIMEOUT INCREASED:
===============================================

Maine timeout 30s se 60s kar diya hai.

Ab Gemini AI ko zyada time milega PDF generate karne ke liye.

===============================================
STILL NOT WORKING?
===============================================

1. Backend FULL logs share karo
2. Browser console ka screenshot
3. .env file ka content (hide API keys)

Detailed guide:
  Read: FIX_PDF_TIMEOUT_ISSUE.md

===============================================
MOST COMMON FIX (95% cases):
===============================================

Sirf .env file mein ye add karo:

VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:5000/api
GEMINI_API_KEY=your-actual-gemini-key

Then:
1. npm run dev:backend
2. npm run dev (frontend)
3. Try again

HO JAYEGA! üöÄ
